</div></div></div></div></div><div id="a18bddd77e452c6b499af980f5063770" class="wb_element wb_element_picture" data-plugin="Picture" title=""><div class="wb_picture_wrap"><div class="wb-picture-wrapper"><img loading="lazy" alt="" src="gallery/dxyz-landing-papertear-4x_compressed-ts1661540570.png?ts=1779023986"></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div id="wb_main_a18bddd8a85d031c03b1af770b1fc6b6" class="wb_element wb-layout-element" data-plugin="LayoutElement"><div class="wb_content wb-layout-vertical"><div id="a18bddd77e452ea7bd5a92bf1e673f67" class="wb_element wb-layout-element" data-plugin="LayoutElement"><div class="wb_content wb-layout-horizontal"><div id="a18bddd77e452f7807f45362e3d350ec" class="wb_element wb-layout-element" data-plugin="LayoutElement"><div class="wb_content wb-layout-vertical"><div id="a18bddd77e453059956c650c33181da3" class="wb_element wb_text_element" data-plugin="TextArea" style=" line-height: normal;"><h3 class="wb-stl-heading3" style="text-align: center;">In my spare time, I like to embark on creative journeys, just for the sake of the process. Not as a means to an end.</h3>
</div><div id="a18bddd77e4531257ba2b18b25feede1" class="wb_element" data-plugin="CustomHtml" style=" overflow: hidden;"><div style="width: 100%; height: 100%; overflow-y: auto;"><style>
html, body {
   max-width: 100%;
   overflow-x: hidden;
}
</style>
</div></div><div id="a18bddd77e4532824b8aff32f263ea1e" class="wb_element wb_text_element" data-plugin="TextArea" style=" line-height: normal;"><h1 class="wb-stl-heading1" style="text-align: center;"><strong><span style="color:rgba(0,0,0,1);">EXPERIENCE </span></strong><span style="color:rgba(0,0,0,1);">AT A GLANCE</span></h1>
</div><div id="a18bddd77e4533b6844764693dcd0046" class="wb_element wb-layout-element" data-plugin="LayoutElement"><div class="wb_content wb-layout-horizontal"><div id="a18bddd77e453499166a16a376198914" class="wb_element wb-layout-element" data-plugin="LayoutElement"><div class="wb_content wb-layout-horizontal"><div id="a18bddd77e4535a4485e68fc1fed3617" class="wb_element wb-layout-element" data-plugin="LayoutElement"><div class="wb_content wb-layout-vertical"><div id="a18bddd77e45363d0a3110e1b1b39cb3" class="wb_element wb-layout-element" data-plugin="LayoutElement"><div class="wb_content wb-layout-vertical"><div id="a18bddd77e4538c8d58f262a881d4a2c" class="wb_element wb_text_element" data-plugin="TextArea" style=" line-height: normal;"><h2 class="wb-stl-heading2"><span style="color:rgba(0,0,0,1);">TikTok</span></h2>
</div></div></div><div id="a18bddd77e46006b3836cb8f709194f7" class="wb_element wb_text_element" data-plugin="TextArea" style=" line-height: normal;"><p class="wb-stl-custom15" style="text-align: center;"><span style="color:rgba(0,0,0,1);">Ever since TikTok became a thing, as a marketer and creative, I have been interested in trying it out. I never really had an idea for content. This was until I remembered an old hobby I had as a 14-year-old boy. Although I did not end up finding it enjoyable, I learned a lot about the platform and made great connections with popular channels in the niche I was dabbling with - ASMR.</span></p>
</div></div></div><div id="a18bddd77e460168be8d3b0da5325eca" class="wb_element wb-layout-element" data-plugin="LayoutElement"><div class="wb_content wb-layout-vertical"><div id="a18bddd77e4602b607b3c25f4b7f7f5c" class="wb_element wb-layout-element" data-plugin="LayoutElement"><div class="wb_content wb-layout-vertical"><div id="a18bddd77e4604f6f9c95a11f0cce799" class="wb_element wb_text_element" data-plugin="TextArea" style=" line-height: normal;"><h2 class="wb-stl-heading2"><span style="color:rgba(255,255,255,1);">YouTube</span></h2>
</div></div></div><div id="a18bddd77e46051bb5c3a29f4a3d03fc" class="wb_element wb_text_element" data-plugin="TextArea" style=" line-height: normal;"><p class="wb-stl-custom15" style="text-align: center;"><font color="#ffffff">A couple of friends I made during my meme advertising days had approached me with ideas to expand their meme pages from Instagram to YouTube. At some point I took a few of them up on their offer. I created several YouTube channels for them, including the branding, channel management (SEO, scheduling, etc.) and video editing. They provided the content and meme know-how.</font></p>
</div></div></div><div id="a18bddd77e4606b885957527e27dd160" class="wb_element wb-layout-element" data-plugin="LayoutElement"><div class="wb_content wb-layout-vertical"><div id="a18bddd77e4607aa2ad7899a70cff918" class="wb_element wb-layout-element" data-plugin="LayoutElement"><div class="wb_content wb-layout-vertical"><div id="a18bddd77e4609b8380451e9d0753cdb" class="wb_element wb_text_element" data-plugin="TextArea" style=" line-height: normal;"><h2 class="wb-stl-heading2">Discord Servers</h2>
</div></div></div><div id="a18bddd77e460aff5598e5ff9317a3f6" class="wb_element wb_text_element" data-plugin="TextArea" style=" line-height: normal;"><p class="wb-stl-custom15" style="text-align: center;">A friend and I had beta-tested a Discord server for the brand, back in 2018, when that was atypical for clothing brands to have. Ever since then I have been wanting to create another Discord community. During my ASMR experiment on TikTok, I noticed that the community on the platform exists but creators hadn't bonded together in a communal space. So I attempted to create an engagement group for them.</p>
</div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div id="a18bddd77e460b13911311d42920b58e" class="wb_element wb-layout-element" data-plugin="LayoutElement"><div class="wb_content wb-layout-vertical"><div id="a18bddd77e460c4b1a7aceacb46871fe" class="wb_element wb-layout-element" data-plugin="LayoutElement"><div class="wb_content wb-layout-vertical"><div id="a18bddd77e460d2f78b400b64e62bb92" class="wb_element wb-layout-element" data-plugin="LayoutElement"><div class="wb_content wb-layout-vertical"><div id="a18bddd77e460f232e103ad1d71cbd76" class="wb_element wb_text_element" data-plugin="TextArea" style=" line-height: normal;"><h2 class="wb-stl-heading2"><span style="color:rgba(0,0,0,1);">TikTok</span></h2>
</div></div></div><div id="a18bddd77e4610dd8621e601a32fca3b" class="wb_element wb_text_element" data-plugin="TextArea" style=" line-height: normal;"><p class="wb-stl-custom15" style="text-align: center;"><span style="color:rgba(0,0,0,1);">Ever since TikTok became a thing, as a marketer and creative, I have been interested in trying it out. I never really had an idea for content. This was until I remembered an old hobby I had as a 14-year-old boy. Although I did not end up finding it enjoyable, I learned a lot about the platform and made great connections with popular channels in the niche I was dabbling with - ASMR.</span></p>
</div></div></div><div id="a18bddd77e461161226fa3d679b0bb50" class="wb_element wb-layout-element" data-plugin="LayoutElement"><div class="wb_content wb-layout-vertical"><div id="a18bddd77e46123f0cd84d6972a8824b" class="wb_element wb-layout-element" data-plugin="LayoutElement"><div class="wb_content wb-layout-vertical"><div id="a18bddd77e46140ba1de8a742e5c8796" class="wb_element wb_text_element" data-plugin="TextArea" style=" line-height: normal;"><h2 class="wb-stl-heading2"><span style="color:rgba(255,255,255,1);">YouTube</span></h2>
</div></div></div><div id="a18bddd77e46153660ccd944c5cdb080" class="wb_element wb_text_element" data-plugin="TextArea" style=" line-height: normal;"><p class="wb-stl-custom15" style="text-align:center"><font color="#ffffff">A couple of friends I made during my meme advertising days had approached me with ideas to expand their meme pages from Instagram to YouTube. At some point I took a few of them up on their offer. I created several YouTube channels for them, including the branding, channel management (SEO, scheduling, etc.) and video editing. They provided the content and meme know-how.</font></p>
</div></div></div><div id="a18bddd77e4616b42ddaf28ebf872da1" class="wb_element wb-layout-element" data-plugin="LayoutElement"><div class="wb_content wb-layout-vertical"><div id="a18bddd77e4617d56ff5fd8f66a2050a" class="wb_element wb-layout-element" data-plugin="LayoutElement"><div class="wb_content wb-layout-vertical"><div id="a18bddd77e4619c3edc264d0bfc90fcd" class="wb_element wb_text_element" data-plugin="TextArea" style=" line-height: normal;"><h2 class="wb-stl-heading2">Discord Servers</h2>
</div></div></div><div id="a18bddd77e461a1f4ce7611540fe1625" class="wb_element wb_text_element" data-plugin="TextArea" style=" line-height: normal;"><p class="wb-stl-custom15" style="text-align: center;">A friend and I had beta-tested a Discord server for the brand, back in 2018, when that was atypical for clothing brands to have. Ever since then I have been wanting to create another Discord community. During my ASMR experiment on TikTok, I noticed that the community on the platform exists but creators hadn't bonded together in a communal space. So I attempted to create an engagement group for them.</p>
</div></div></div></div></div><div id="a18bddd77e461bddf7650033e2690af2" class="wb_element wb_text_element" data-plugin="TextArea" style=" line-height: normal;"><h1 class="wb-stl-heading1" style="text-align: center;"><strong><span style="color:rgba(0,0,0,1);">ABILITIES </span></strong><span style="color:rgba(0,0,0,1);">AT A GLANCE</span></h1>
</div><div id="a18bddd77e461c8f1165171af29cdedb" class="wb_element wb-layout-element" data-plugin="LayoutElement"><div class="wb_content wb-layout-vertical"><div id="a18bddd77e461d7cbbb99ff252c7288f" class="wb_element wb_element_picture" data-plugin="Picture" title=""><div class="wb_picture_wrap"><div class="wb-picture-wrapper"><img loading="lazy" alt="" src="gallery_gen/e577818cacaf88fe0f656816906c4bc6_1580x536_fit.png?ts=1779023987"></div></div></div></div></div><div id="a18bddd77e461ebc4d7d1b9f250d9faa" class="wb_element wb-layout-element" data-plugin="LayoutElement"><div class="wb_content wb-layout-vertical"><div id="a18bddd77e461f78a6f9db7dfdf5623e" class="wb_element wb_text_element" data-plugin="TextArea" style=" line-height: normal;"><h1 class="wb-stl-heading1" style="text-align: center;"><strong><span style="color:rgba(0,0,0,1);">VISUAL PORTFOLIO</span></strong></h1>
</div></div></div><div id="a18bddd77e46205b04f5ac2a52e77a49" class="wb_element wb-layout-element" data-plugin="LayoutElement"><div class="wb_content wb-layout-vertical"><div id="a18bddd77e462118c3dce956d0f9c425" class="wb_element wb_text_element" data-plugin="TextArea" style=" line-height: normal;"><h2 class="wb-stl-heading2" style="text-align: center;"><strong><span style="color:rgba(0,0,0,1);">Tingle Cartel<br>
(Discord Server)</span></strong></h2>
</div><div id="a18bddd77e4622ced2646e085ed926ab" class="wb_element wb_text_element" data-plugin="TextArea" style=" line-height: normal;"><h1 class="wb-stl-custom11" style="text-align: center;"><strong><span style="color:rgba(71,71,71,1);">Community for TikTok ASMRtists to connect &amp; grow.</span></strong></h1>

<h1 class="wb-stl-custom11" style="text-align: center;"> </h1>

